WEBVTT FILE

1
00:00:00.001 --> 00:00:06.000
He was a brave man, however, and
putting aside all fear went forward dauntlessly.

2
00:00:06.500 --> 00:00:16.000
Crunch, crunch! He stepped now on the dragon’s body,
now between its coils, and without
even one glance backward he went on his way.

3
00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:21.000
He had only gone a few steps when
he heard someone calling him from behind.

4
00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:33.000
On turning back he was
really surprised to see that the
monster dragon had entirely
disappeared and in its place was a
strange-looking man who was
formally bowing to the ground.

5
00:00:34.000 --> 00:00:44.000
His red hair streamed over his
shoulders and was surmounted by
a crown in the shape of a dragon’s
head, and his sea-green dress was
patterned with shells.

6
00:00:44.500 --> 00:00:51.000
Hidesato knew at once that this was no
ordinary mortal and he wondered
much at the strange occurrence.
